overview: This series brings the biggest names in the adult industry together with some big bad men. Featured cover girl Ivy Wolfe likes to gamble, but there is only one thing she wants from this high-stakes game she's playing. Ivy leaves her fate to the roulette wheel and hopes her opponent might take her body for a spin. Lexi Belle, Elsa Jean, and Anissa Kate are all here to show you why they belong on the A-list.
title: Stars 3
